Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: “Kamala Harris was basically a National Joke until there was an explosion of media propaganda on her behalf about 35 days ago when the Democrats imposed her on the Party and the Country without having a single vote and one of the reasons is because every time she spoke off script as Vice President it was a gigantic embarrassment!” Glenn Greenwald on Jesse Watters Primetime
